column1: Meghan Markle says "no one in the world" loves her more than Prince Harry — and the feeling is very much mutual!
He loves me so boldly, fully, she tells Harper's Bazaar.
He also has a different perspective because he sees media that I wouldn't. No one in the world loves me more than him, so I know he's always going to make sure that he has my back.
As for the ridicule she faces
column3: "I love being able to… play in the sandbox with my kids and to play in the front row at a show."
